The paper discusses the technical challenges associated with the deployment of heterogeneous networks, which are wireless networks consisting of a mix of macrocells, remote radio heads, and low-power nodes such as picocells, femtocells, and relays. The focus of the paper is on the standardization activities within the 3GPP related to enhanced intercell interference coordination. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Other likely sub-categories include cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AR (Hardware Architecture).
